column5: HI JUST WONDERING WHEN THE SEASON ENDED FOR WALLEYES ON THE BOQ PLANNING ON HITTING IT NEXT WEEKEND GOT ROOM IN THE TRUCK IF ANYONE WANTS TO TAG ALONG

February 29th midnight is closing I believe.  Easton
THANKS  AND FORGOT LEAVING FROM HAMILTON
